creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of Short Poetry Collection 141 by Various.
Read in English by Tanko Hunor; Ian King; Algy Pug; Son of the Exiles; Bruce Kachuk; DomBombadil; Garth Burton; Winston Tharp; Larry Wilson; Leonard Wilson; Andani Thakhathi; Shakira Searle
This is a collection of 27 poems read by LibriVox volunteers for February 2015. This collection includes the following: Alone, Edgar Allan Poe The Ashes in the Sea, George Sterling Ballad for Gloom, Ezra Pound The Cultured Constable, C. J. Dennis The Disinterred Warrior, William Cullen Bryant Elegy in a Country Churchyard, G. K. Chesterton Famam Librosque Cano, Ezra Pound February, George Milner The Future Life, William Cullen Bryant Gerontion, T. S. Eliot Human Frailty, William Cowper In Tempore Senectutis, Ezra Pound The Lay of the Lover’s Friend, William Edmondstoune Aytoun Liberty, James Allen Life’s Mirror, Mary Ainge de Vere Long I sought Thee, James Allen Mise en Scène, Amy Lowell A Noiseless Patient Spider, Walt Whitman The Philosopher, Edna St. Vincent Millay Practice and Perception, James Allen Robin Hood, John Keats The Spider and the Fly, Mary Howitt To F. C., Mortimer Collins To His Valentine on St. Valentine's Day, Robert Herrick The Windhover, Gerard Manley Hopkins Winter's Turning, Amy Lowell Witch-Wife, Edna St. Vincent Millay
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
